is erweitert. Es greift alle notwendigen Aspekte auf, um Architekten und Planern einen unterstützenden Einblick in die Thematik zu geben.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn German.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 29. Nov 2021) 0aPrisonsxDesign and constructionvHandbooks, manuals, etc. 0aPrisonsxHandbooks, manuals, etcxDesign and construction. 4aArchitektur. 4aEntwurf. 4aGebäudelehre. 4aGefängnis. 4aGefängnisbau. 4aJustizanstalt. 4aStrafvollzug. 7aARCHITECTURE / General.2bisacsh08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDGBA Architecture, Design and Arts 2000 - 2014z9783110635690oZDB-23-GAA0 cprintz978399043310240uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/978399043719340uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9783990437193423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9783990437193/original  aEBA_BACKALL  aEBA_CL_AD  aEBA_DGALL  aEBA_EBKALL  aEBA_SSHALL  aEBA_STMALL  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aPDA11SSHE  aPDA12STME  aPDA5EBK  aZDB-23-GAAc2000d2014